- Map response: `message.content[0].type === "text" ? message.content[0].text : ""` for text, `message.usage.input_tokens` / `message.usage.output_tokens` for usage

### 3. `src/llm/providers/openai.ts`
- Import `OpenAI` from `openai`
- Import types from `../types`
- Export class `OpenAIProvider` implementing `LLMProvider`
- Constructor takes `apiKey: string`, creates `new OpenAI({ apiKey })`
- `chat()` method calls `this.client.chat.completions.create()` with:
  - `model: request.model`
  - `max_tokens: request.maxTokens`
  - `messages: [{ role: "system", content: request.system }, ...request.messages]`
- Map response: `response.choices[0]?.message?.content ?? ""` for text
- For usage: `response.usage?.prompt_tokens ?? 0` / `response.usage?.completion_tokens ?? 0`

### 4. `src/llm/providers/google.ts`
- Import `GoogleGenerativeAI` from `@google/generative-ai`
- Import types from `../types`
- Export class `GoogleProvider` implementing `LLMProvider`
- Constructor takes `apiKey: string`, creates `new GoogleGenerativeAI(apiKey)`
- `chat()` method:
  - Get model: `this.client.getGenerativeModel({ model: request.model, systemInstruction: request.system })`
  - Map messages to Google format: `{ role: msg.role === "assistant" ? "model" : "user", parts: [{ text: msg.content }] }`
  - Call `model.generateContent({ contents, generationConfig: { maxOutputTokens: request.maxTokens } })`
  - Map response: `result.response.text()` for text
  - For usage: `result.response.usageMetadata?.promptTokenCount ?? 0` / `result.response.usageMetadata?.candidatesTokenCount ?? 0`

### 5. `src/llm/index.ts`
```typescript
export type { LLMProvider, LLMRequest, LLMResponse } from "./types";
import type { LLMProvider } from "./types";

export function createProvider(provider: string, apiKey: string): LLMProvider {
  switch (provider) {
    case "anthropic": {
      const { AnthropicProvider } = require("./providers/anthropic");
      return new AnthropicProvider(apiKey);
    }
    case "openai": {
      const { OpenAIProvider } = require("./providers/openai");
      return new OpenAIProvider(apiKey);
    }
    case "google": {
      const { GoogleProvider } = require("./providers/google");
      return new GoogleProvider(apiKey);
    }
    default:
      throw new Error(`Unknown LLM provider: "${provider}". Supported providers: anthropic, openai, google`);
  }
}
```

