2. Change function signature: `client?: Anthropic` → `client?: LLMProvider`
3. Remove the fallback client construction (`client ?? new Anthropic(...)`) — just use `client` directly. The caller (src/index.ts) will always provide it. But keep it safe: if no client, throw an error:
   ```typescript
